<i>You got 30 seconds.!</i>

06:20.046 --> 06:23.072
After tomorrow, there's not
anybody that can keep us apart.

06:28.688 --> 06:32.283
<i>I said, out.!</i>

06:32.358 --> 06:34.883
Just take your skinny, pale behind
out of here...

06:34.961 --> 06:37.828
<i>fore I call yo'mama and tell her
what you've been up to.</i>

06:37.897 --> 06:41.594
