I belong here.

10:09.609 --> 10:12.442
You got me worried big time. All right,
Gooshie. What are you worried about?

10:12.511 --> 10:15.708
Let's get to work on this.
Sam, do me a favor. What?

10:15.781 --> 10:20.741
Stay away from Abigail.

10:20.820 --> 10:22.879
Okay?
Okay.

10:28.728 --> 10:30.719
<i>It had been 11 years,</i>

10:30.796 --> 10:34.823
<i>and Abigail had grown from a frightened
child into a glorious young woman.</i>

10:34.900 --> 10:40.099
<i>Al's request to stay away from her was as absurd
as asking the sun not to rise on their wedding day.</i>

10:40.172 --> 10:42.163
<i>I know you're gonna be here, Al.</i>

10:42.241 --> 10:46.177
The question is, how close to the wire
are you gonna- put me?

10:50.216 --> 10:52.912
