the last one to see him.

12:13.566 --> 12:15.830
<i>She was with me last night.
Sam, watch it.</i>

12:15.901 --> 12:18.699
It's 1966 in a small Southern town.

12:18.771 --> 12:22.832
She w-was with m-me last night.

12:22.908 --> 12:25.342
<i>Till midnight, and then he went home.</i>

12:26.479 --> 12:30.438
Abigail, did you sit
the Takins boy last night?

12:30.516 --> 12:34.350
<i>Yes, but I left at 9:30.
Mr. And Mrs. Takins came home.</i>

12:34.420 --> 12:36.650
- They paid me, and then I left.
