13:42.188 --> 13:46.147
<i>Well, you do that. But then the two of
you get across the street, all right?</i>

13:47.626 --> 13:53.394
Honey, you better start believin' in
bad luck, 'cause it sure believes in you.

13:58.270 --> 14:00.261
This can't be happenin'. Not today.

14:00.339 --> 14:03.502
