We're gonna find him, aren't we?

14:03.576 --> 14:05.942
I would die if something
happened to that little boy.

14:06.011 --> 14:08.536
We are gonna f-find him,

14:08.614 --> 14:12.948
and then we're gonna get married
just as soon as you can say-

14:13.018 --> 14:16.454
Jackrabbit.

14:16.522 --> 14:19.548
Okay?
Now, I promise.

14:20.759 --> 14:22.727
Get goin'.
I'll see you in the front.

14:22.795 --> 14:24.786
Okay. Get goin'.

